      <title>英国工党暂停候选人资格，因其对自身不利进行投注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/uk-s-labour-suspends-candidate-for-betting-against-himself</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国主要反对党工党暂停了一位在即将举行的大选前对自己进行押注的候选人的资格，这是有关选举押注的最新争议，此前此类押注仅困扰着里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的保守党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/uk-s-labour-suspends-candidate-for-betting-against-himself</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 21:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
