    <item>
      <title>SEC 仍在考虑就新对冲基金规则在法庭上采取的下一步行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/sec-still-weighing-next-steps-in-court-over-new-hedge-fund-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会主席加里·根斯勒称，华尔街最高监管机构仍在评估下一步措施，试图迫使对冲基金和私募股权公司披露更多有关其费用的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/sec-still-weighing-next-steps-in-court-over-new-hedge-fund-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 19:27:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博阿兹·温斯坦称拜登比特朗普更适合债券市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/boaz-weinstein-says-biden-is-better-for-bond-market-than-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[萨巴资本管理公司 (Saba Capital Management) 的博阿兹·温斯坦 (Boaz Weinstein) 在周二的彭博投资会议上表示，总统乔·拜登的连任对美国债券市场来说将比唐纳德·特朗普第二次担任总统更有利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/boaz-weinstein-says-biden-is-better-for-bond-market-than-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 19:25:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SpaceX 猎鹰重型火箭发射卫星追踪太阳风暴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/spacex-s-falcon-heavy-to-launch-us-satellite-to-track-sun-storms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SpaceX 的猎鹰重型火箭是世界上最强大的运载火箭之一，它于周二发射升空，将一颗新的美国卫星送入轨道，该卫星旨在帮助气象预报员监测大规模太阳风暴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/spacex-s-falcon-heavy-to-launch-us-satellite-to-track-sun-storms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:47:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利针对反腐监督机构和调查媒体展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/hungary-launches-probe-against-graft-watchdog-in-orban-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班设立的一个国家机构已开始对反腐监督机构透明国际和一家新闻网站进行调查，这是针对批评其政权的群体的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/hungary-launches-probe-against-graft-watchdog-in-orban-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 14:40:50 GMT</pubDate>
